high_descs: Head to the exit on the left and turn left to reach the kitchen on the right to face the sink.
Pick up the black pot from the sink.
Turn around to reach the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge and take it out.
Turn around to reach the microwave.
Put the pot in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put the cooled pot in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go near the sink.
Take the pot from the sink table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Put the pot into the refrigerator and cooled it.
Then take the microwave out and go near the oven table.
Put the pot into the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Placed the pot into the microwave from the table.

high_descs: Walk straight to the wall on your left, turn left, walk straight outside the room, then go towards the shelf to your left and then go to the sink on your right.
Pick up the pot on the sink.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the pot in the fridge, let it cool for a while and then take it out.
Turn around and go to the microwave to the left of the sink.
Put the pot in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cool pot inside a microwave.
